<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Tarifa Reseller · PcComponentes</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --primary: #e2001a;
    --primary-dark: #b80015;
    --bg: #f5f5f5;
    --card-bg: #ffffff;
    --border: #e0e0e0;
    --text: #1a1a1a;
    --text-muted: #666;
    --top-color: #f59e0b;
    --success: #16a34a;
    --mid: #d97706;
    --low: #dc2626;
    --sidebar-w: 240px;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); }

  /* HEADER */
  header {
    background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary);
    padding: 0 24px;
    height: 60px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  }
  .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; text-decoration: none; }
  .logo-badge {
    background: var(--primary); color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .logo-text { font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; color: var(--text); }
  .logo-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-left: 4px; }
  .header-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .btn-help {
    background: none; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-muted);
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 6px 12px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px;
  }
  .btn-help:hover { background: var(--bg); }

  /* LAYOUT */
  .layout { display: flex; min-height: calc(100vh - 60px); }

  /* SIDEBAR */
  aside {
    width: var(--sidebar-w);
    background: #fff;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 20px 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    overflow-y: auto;
    height: calc(100vh - 60px);
    position: sticky; top: 60px;
  }
  .sidebar-section { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .sidebar-label {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .slider-wrap { padding: 4px 0; }
  .margin-display {
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  input[type=range] {
    width: 100%; accent-color: var(--primary);
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .slider-hint { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 6px; text-align: center; }
  select, .search-input {
    width: 100%; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 13px; background: #fff; color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  select:focus, .search-input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); }
  .checkbox-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .checkbox-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; }
  .checkbox-item input { accent-color: var(--primary); width: 15px; height: 15px; cursor: pointer; }
  .filter-chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; margin-top: 8px; }
  .chip {
    background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 99px; padding: 3px 10px; font-size: 11px;
    cursor: pointer; transition: all .15s;
  }
  .chip.active, .chip:hover { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border-color: var(--primary); }

  /* MAIN */
  main { flex: 1; min-width: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  /* TOOLBAR */
  .toolbar {
    background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 12px 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap; position: sticky; top: 60px; z-index: 90;
  }
  .search-wrap { flex: 1; min-width: 200px; position: relative; }
  .search-wrap input {
    width: 100%; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 12px 8px 36px; font-size: 14px; background: var(--bg);
  }
  .search-wrap input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); background: #fff; }
  .search-icon { position: absolute; left: 11px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); color: #aaa; }
  .result-count { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); white-space: nowrap; }
  .view-btns { display: flex; gap: 4px; }
  .view-btn {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: #fff;
    border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; display: flex;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all .15s;
  }
  .view-btn.active { background: var(--primary); border-color: var(--primary); color: #fff; }
  .btn-select {
    background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border: none;
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 7px 16px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600; transition: background .15s;
  }
  .btn-select:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); }
  .btn-select.active { background: #333; }
  .btn-export {
    background: #fff; color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 7px 14px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px;
    transition: background .15s;
  }
  .btn-export:hover { background: var(--bg); }
  select.sort-sel {
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 7px 10px;
    font-size: 13px; background: #fff; cursor: pointer; min-width: 180px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* CONTENT */
  .content { padding: 20px; flex: 1; overflow: auto; }

  /* TABLE VIEW */
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
  thead th {
    background: #f8f8f8; padding: 10px 14px; text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: var(--text-muted);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; transition: background .1s; }
  tbody tr:hover { background: #fafafa; }
  tbody tr.selected { background: #fff5f5; }
  tbody td { padding: 10px 14px; vertical-align: middle; }
  .td-check { width: 32px; text-align: center; }
  .td-check input { accent-color: var(--primary); width: 15px; height: 15px; cursor: pointer; }
  .prod-name { font-weight: 500; max-width: 340px; line-height: 1.3; }
  .prod-brand { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }
  .badge-top { font-size: 11px; }
  .price { font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .pvpr { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: line-through; font-size: 12px; }
  .pvp-sug { font-weight: 600; color: var(--success); white-space: nowrap; }
  .margin-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 99px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .margin-high { background: #dcfce7; color: #16a34a; }
  .margin-mid { background: #fef3c7; color: #d97706; }
  .margin-low { background: #fee2e2; color: #dc2626; }
  .stock-badge {
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .stock-ok { color: var(--success); }
  .stock-low { color: var(--mid); }
  .stock-out { color: #aaa; }
  .link-btn {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 8px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .link-btn:hover { background: var(--bg); }

  /* CARD VIEW */
  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .card {
    background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; position: relative;
    transition: box-shadow .15s, transform .1s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.1); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .card.selected { border-color: var(--primary); background: #fff8f8; }
  .card-check {
    position: absolute; top: 12px; right: 12px;
  }
  .card-check input { accent-color: var(--primary); width: 16px; height: 16px; cursor: pointer; }
  .card-top { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .card-brand { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .card-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.35; margin-bottom: 10px; min-height: 36px; }
  .card-prices { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .card-price { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); }
  .card-pvpr { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: line-through; }
  .card-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .card-pvp-sug { font-size: 12px; color: var(--success); font-weight: 600; }
  .card-footer { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 10px; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }

  /* BOTTOM BAR (selection mode) */
  .bottom-bar {
    position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; padding: 14px 24px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; z-index: 200;
    transform: translateY(100%); transition: transform .3s;
    box-shadow: 0 -4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
  }
  .bottom-bar.visible { transform: translateY(0); }
  .bottom-bar .sel-count { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
  .bottom-bar .sel-total {
    font-size: 12px; color: #aaa;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .bottom-bar .sel-total strong { color: #fff; font-size: 16px; }
  .bottom-bar .spacer { flex: 1; }
  .btn-clear { background: none; border: 1px solid #555; color: #aaa; border-radius: 6px; padding: 7px 14px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; }
  .btn-clear:hover { border-color: #aaa; color: #fff; }
  .btn-export-sel { background: var(--primary); border: none; color: #fff; border-radius: 6px; padding: 7px 16px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; }
  .btn-copy-links { background: #333; border: 1px solid #555; color: #fff; border-radius: 6px; padding: 7px 14px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; }

  /* MODAL */
  .modal-overlay {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    z-index: 300; display: none; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
  .modal {
    background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; max-width: 540px; width: 90%;
    padding: 28px; max-height: 80vh; overflow-y: auto;
  }
  .modal h2 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--text); }
  .modal-close { float: right; background: none; border: none; font-size: 22px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .step { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .step-num {
    width: 28px; height: 28px; background: var(--primary); color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .step-text { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .step-text strong { color: var(--text); }

  /* EMPTY STATE */
  .empty { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .empty-icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 12px; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    text-align: center; padding: 16px; font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: #fff; margin-top: auto;
  }
  footer a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    :root { --sidebar-w: 0px; }
    aside { display: none; }
    .toolbar { padding: 8px 12px; }
    .content { padding: 12px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <a class="logo" href="https://www.pccomponentes.com/resellers" target="_blank">
    <span class="logo-badge">PC</span>
    <span class="logo-text">PcComponentes</span>
    <span class="logo-sub">Programa Resellers ↗</span>
  </a>
  <div class="header-right">
    <button class="btn-help" onclick="document.getElementById('modal').classList.add('open')">Cómo usar</button>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="layout">
  <!-- SIDEBAR -->
  <aside>
    <!-- Calculadora margen -->
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <div class="sidebar-label">Calculadora de margen</div>
      <div class="slider-wrap">
        <div class="margin-display" id="marginDisplay">20%</div>
        <input type="range" id="marginSlider" min="5" max="60" value="20" step="1">
        <div class="slider-hint">PVP sugerido = Precio Reseller ÷ (1 − margen)</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Marca -->
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <div class="sidebar-label">Marca</div>
      <select id="filterMarca">
        <option value="">Todas las marcas</option>
        <option value="Alurin">Alurin</option>
<option value="Forgeon">Forgeon</option>
<option value="Nilait">Nilait</option>
<option value="Origial">Origial</option>
<option value="Owlotech">Owlotech</option>
<option value="PcCom">PcCom</option>
<option value="PcCom Essential">PcCom Essential</option>
<option value="Tempest">Tempest</option>
<option value="Voltrock">Voltrock</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <!-- Categoría -->
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <div class="sidebar-label">Categoría</div>
      <select id="filterCategoria">
        <option value="">Todas las categorías</option>
        <option value="Hogar">Hogar</option>
<option value="Home">Home</option>
<option value="Home Entertainment- Audio, Foto y Vídeo">Home Entertainment- Audio, Foto y Vídeo</option>
<option value="IT-Componentes">IT-Componentes</option>
<option value="IT-Computing Hardware">IT-Computing Hardware</option>
<option value="IT-Periféricos Hardware y Conectividad">IT-Periféricos Hardware y Conectividad</option>
<option value="IT-Periféricos y gaming">IT-Periféricos y gaming</option>
<option value="Mobility">Mobility</option>
<option value="Ocio y movilidad">Ocio y movilidad</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <!-- Disponibilidad -->
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <div class="sidebar-label">Disponibilidad</div>
      <div class="checkbox-group">
        <label class="checkbox-item">
          <input type="checkbox" id="filterStock"> Solo con stock
        </label>
        <label class="checkbox-item">
          <input type="checkbox" id="filterTop"> ⭐ Solo oportunidades top
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Margen potencial -->
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <div class="sidebar-label">Margen potencial</div>
      <div class="filter-chips">
        <span class="chip active" data-margin="all">Todos</span>
        <span class="chip" data-margin="high">Alto ≥ 30%</span>
        <span class="chip" data-margin="mid">Medio 15–30%</span>
        <span class="chip" data-margin="low">Bajo &lt; 15%</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <!-- MAIN -->
  <main>
    <!-- TOOLBAR -->
    <div class="toolbar">
      <div class="search-wrap">
        <span class="search-icon">🔍</span>
        <input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="Buscar por nombre, marca, referencia…">
      </div>
      <select class="sort-sel" id="sortSel">
        <option value="name">Ordenar: Nombre A→Z</option>
        <option value="price_asc">Precio: menor a mayor</option>
        <option value="price_desc">Precio: mayor a menor</option>
        <option value="margin_desc">Margen: mayor a menor</option>
        <option value="stock_desc">Más stock primero</option>
        <option value="top_first">Oportunidades top primero</option>
      </select>
      <span class="result-count" id="resultCount">— productos</span>
      <div class="view-btns">
        <button class="view-btn active" id="btnTable" title="Vista tabla" onclick="setView('table')">☰</button>
        <button class="view-btn" id="btnCards" title="Vista tarjetas" onclick="setView('cards')">⊞</button>
      </div>
      <button class="btn-select" id="btnSelect" onclick="toggleSelect()">Seleccionar</button>
      <button class="btn-export" onclick="exportCSV()">Exportar CSV</button>
    </div>

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <div class="content" id="mainContent">
      <!-- Populated by JS -->
    </div>

    <footer>
      Tarifa exclusiva para el programa Resellers de PcComponentes &nbsp;·&nbsp;
      <a href="https://www.pccomponentes.com/resellers" target="_blank">www.pccomponentes.com/resellers</a>
    </footer>
  </main>
</div>

<!-- BOTTOM BAR -->
<div class="bottom-bar" id="bottomBar">
  <span class="sel-count" id="selCount">0 productos seleccionados</span>
  <span class="sel-total">
    Precio total estimado (precio Reseller)<br>
    <strong id="selTotal">0,00 €</strong>
  </span>
  <span class="spacer"></span>
  <button class="btn-clear" onclick="clearSelection()">Limpiar</button>
  <button class="btn-export-sel" onclick="exportSelectionCSV()">Exportar selección</button>
  <button class="btn-copy-links" onclick="copyLinks()">Copiar links</button>
</div>

<!-- MODAL -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal" onclick="if(event.target===this)this.classList.remove('open')">
  <div class="modal">
    <button class="modal-close" onclick="document.getElementById('modal').classList.remove('open')">×</button>
    <h2>Cómo usar la Tarifa Reseller</h2>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Busca y filtra productos</strong><br>Usa la barra de búsqueda para encontrar por nombre o marca. Filtra por marca, categoría, disponibilidad de stock o nivel de margen desde el panel izquierdo.</div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Calcula tu precio de venta</strong><br>Mueve el slider <strong>Margen objetivo</strong> para fijar el porcentaje que quieres ganar. La columna <em>PVP sugerido</em> se actualiza en tiempo real.</div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Identifica las mejores oportunidades</strong><br>Los productos marcados con ⭐ Top combinan buen margen y stock disponible. Filtra por <em>Solo oportunidades top</em> para verlos de golpe.</div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">4</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Cambia de vista</strong><br>Usa los botones ⊞ ☰ de la barra superior para alternar entre vista tabla y vista tarjetas.</div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">5</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Crea tu lista de pedido</strong><br>Pulsa <strong>Seleccionar</strong> para activar el modo selección. Marca los productos — la barra inferior muestra el total acumulado. Desde ahí puedes exportar como CSV o copiar los enlaces.</div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">6</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Exporta los datos</strong><br>El botón <strong>Exportar CSV</strong> descarga todos los productos visibles con los filtros activos, incluyendo precios, márgenes y PVP sugerido.</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

